program tree


class PROGRAM:
	- Handles input
		- sends input to appropriate section.
	- Has a bunch of screens
	- Has a current screen, where all the input and displays will be interfacing
	- Has a main menu. This is displayed over the current screen, rendered after it.
	- only 1 screen is displayed at a time.


class SCREEN:
	- Has the ability to have special menus
	- Has the ability to have buttons.
	- Has the ability to have a menu bar.
	- These things are what populate the SCREEN class:
		- Buttons
		- Text
		- Images
		- 3D Renders.
		- Draw areas
		- Drop down boxes
		- Lock panels



		
